      {
        "title": "Setup Required First",
        "content": "```bash\nnpm install --save-dev jest jest-environment-jsdom @testing-library/react @testing-library/jest-dom babel-jest\n```\n\nAdd to `package.json`:\n```json\n\"jest\": {\n  \"testEnvironment\": \"jsdom\",\n  \"setupFilesAfterFramework\": [\"@testing-library/jest-dom\"]\n}\n```\n\nStart with **`LiteralMode`** and **`BriefService`** -- pure functions, zero mocking required, highest logic density.",
